Ref:
When you pass the logical ID of this resource to the intrinsic Ref function, Ref returns the name of the Multi-Region Access Point.

For more information about using the Ref function, see Ref.

GetAtt.Description: The alias for the Multi-Region Access Point. For more information about the distinction between the name and the alias of an Multi-Region Access Point, see Managing Multi-Region Access Points in the Amazon S3 User Guide.
The timestamp of when the Multi-Region Access Point is created.
